---
title: "US26 — Share achievements to social media"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>WorkoutSummaryScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>CreateWorkoutSharePost · ShareWorkoutToSocial
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Post (workout_share)
  A->>B: toggle "Share to Social" on, pick platform
  B->>C: share(caption, platform)
  C->>E: new Post with public caption only
  note right of E: private notes are<br/>never shared
  E-->>C: post created
  C-->>B: share to Facebook / Instagram / Twitter / TikTok
  B-->>A: OS share sheet opens with message
  note over E: post via SocialGateway - platform share via SocialShareGateway
